sep.seeter.net.message

Class SeetsReply

  • java.lang.Object
    • sep.seeter.net.message.SeetsReply
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, Message

    public final class SeetsReply
extends java.lang.Object
implements Message
    A SEET-REPLY message: the server reply to a SEET request: the list of lines recorded by the server for the specified topic, listed from the specified index.

    Instances of this class are immutable.
